Opening up all three Heirlooms (Wraith's Kunai knives, Bloodhound's Raven's Bite axe and the Lifeline's Shock Sticks) within 39 cases. Bloodhound Heirloom was unlocked from a free case that was recieved from the Season 3 Battle Pass, the Lifeline Heirloom was unlocked when i purchased the 24 Apex Packs necessary to unlock all the skins from the event plus the Heirloom. Afterwards, having leftover Apex Coins, decided to actually purchase 14 more cases and on the very last case, unlocking the Wraith's Heirloom. In total it took me 39 cases counting the free case from the battle pass.

Unedited video: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/501469032

🛠️ Apex Legends Battle Royale Settings: 
Resolution: 1920 x 1080 
Sensitivity: 1.5 (ADS Multiplier 1.2)
Mouse/Keyboard: Finalmouse Ultralight Sunset  / Razer BlackWidow Chroma V2
Field of view: 104 (all low graphics settings)
